B%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-thu%E1%BB%B7-khi%E1%BB%83n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-fJ7dsvdhURP9WS38n6MV1g">Thướng thuỷ khiển hoài - 上水遣懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/T%C3%ADch-quang-%C3%A2m/poem-tqXC72MZwuHwR9u3-I22iA">Tích quang âm - 惜光陰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Chu-V%C4%83n-An/poem-w0GgquYtfAVcoL3oiMfAsQ">Vịnh Chu Văn An - 詠朱文安</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-thi-X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch/poem-mnn5Yw2u1F5QXWi8KVeU5A">Vịnh sử thi - Xích Bích - 詠史詩－赤壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/author-QGyhycNQKN2UVF9H-N6Zaw">Hồ Tằng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
